sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    %% Flow 1: TrustyAI Prediction Monitoring
    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
    Note over Client,DB: Flow 1 - TrustyAI Prediction Monitoring
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServeISVC as KServe InferenceService<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant InfLogger as KServe InferenceLogger
    participant TASProxy as TrustyAI kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS(service-ca)
    participant TASService as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as PostgreSQL / PVC<br/>TLS (optional)
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Client->>KServeISVC: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KServeISVC->>InfLogger: Forward prediction payload
    InfLogger->>TASProxy: POST prediction data<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS(service-ca)
    TASProxy->>TASService: Forward (localhost)
    TASService->>DB: Store prediction + metadata<br/>DB credentials from Secret
    Prom->>TASProxy: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP via ServiceMonitor
    end

    %% Flow 2: LMEval Job Execution
    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
    Note over User,ModelEndpoint: Flow 2 - LMEval Job Execution
    participant User as User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LMESCtrl as LMES Controller
    participant KueueWL as Kueue Workload
    participant LMEvalPod as LMEval Pod<br/>(Driver + lm-eval)
    participant Driver as LMES Driver<br/>18080/TCP HTTP (pod-internal)
    participant ModelEndpoint as Model Endpoint<br/>(VLLM/OpenAI)<br/>HTTPS

    User->>K8sAPI: Create LMEvalJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>LMESCtrl: Watch event: LMEvalJob created
    LMESCtrl->>KueueWL: Create Workload CR<br/>GPU quota scheduling
    KueueWL-->>LMESCtrl: Workload admitted
    LMESCtrl->>LMEvalPod: Create Pod<br/>(driver init + lm-eval container)
    LMESCtrl->>Driver: GET /status<br/>18080/TCP HTTP (pod-internal)
    Driver-->>LMESCtrl: Progress + status
    LMEvalPod->>ModelEndpoint: Evaluate model<br/>HTTPS, Auth: API key
    ModelEndpoint-->>LMEvalPod: Evaluation results
    end

    %% Flow 3: EvalHub Evaluation Pipeline
    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
    Note over MCPClient,TenantNS: Flow 3 - EvalHub Evaluation Pipeline
    participant MCPClient as User / MCP Client
    participant EHRoute as EvalHub Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS reencrypt
    participant EHProxy as EvalHub kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS(service-ca)
    participant EHApi as EvalHub API<br/>8444/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    participant TenantNS as Batch Job<br/>(tenant namespace)
    participant FailReconciler as Job Failure Reconciler

    MCPClient->>EHRoute: POST /api/v1/evaluations<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    EHRoute->>EHProxy: Forward (reencrypt)<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    EHProxy->>EHApi: Forward (localhost)<br/>X-Forwarded-User header
    Note over EHProxy: SAR check: evalhubs/proxy
    EHApi->>TenantNS: Create Batch Job<br/>ServiceAccount
    TenantNS-->>FailReconciler: Watch: Job failed
    FailReconciler->>EHProxy: POST failure event<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Operator SA Bearer Token
    end

    %% Flow 4: Guardrails Orchestrator Auto-Configuration
    rect rgb(255, 230, 255)
    Note over GUser,DetectorISVC: Flow 4 - Guardrails Orchestrator Auto-Configuration
    participant GUser as User
    participant GK8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant GORCHCtrl as GORCH Controller
    participant ISVCs as KServe InferenceServices<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant GORCHDeploy as Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8432/TCP HTTPS
    participant GORCHRoute as Orchestrator Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS reencrypt
    participant DetectorISVC as Detector InferenceServices<br/>gRPC/HTTP

    GUser->>GK8s: Create GuardrailsOrchestrator CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    GK8s->>GORCHCtrl: Watch event: GORCH created
    GORCHCtrl->>ISVCs: Watch & discover detectors<br/>by label matching
    ISVCs-->>GORCHCtrl: Detector endpoints + TLS certs
    GORCHCtrl->>GORCHCtrl: Generate config ConfigMap<br/>(content hash for change detection)
    GORCHCtrl->>GORCHDeploy: Create/Update Deployment<br/>+ kube-rbac-proxy sidecar
    MCPClient->>GORCHRoute: POST /api/v1/chat<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    GORCHRoute->>GORCHDeploy: Forward (reencrypt)
    GORCHDeploy->>DetectorISVC: Forward to detectors<br/>gRPC/HTTP, TLS (configurable)
    end
